<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>com.claude_code_ui.app</id>
  <name>Claude Code UI</name>
  <summary>A web-based UI for Claude Code CLI</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Claude Code UI is a comprehensive desktop application that provides a user-friendly interface for 
      the Claude Code CLI. It combines the power of AI-assisted coding with an intuitive graphical interface, 
      making it accessible to developers of all experience levels.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Full-featured terminal with Claude Code CLI integration</li>
      <li>Project management and file operations</li>
      <li>Secure authentication and session management</li>
      <li>Cross-platform desktop application built with Electron</li>
      <li>Clean, modern interface with hidden menu bar by default</li>
      <li>Built-in file browser and project explorer</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Whether you're working on personal projects or professional development, Claude Code UI streamlines 
      your workflow by providing direct access to AI-powered coding assistance through an elegant desktop interface.
    </p>
  </description>
  
